* {{Timeline-event |date={{Start date|2019|09|25|df=y}} |event= EDF announces that the total cost of the power station was likely to rise by up to £2.9{{nbsp}}billion and the total bill could be more than £22{{nbsp}}billion}}<ref name=ja/>
