* {{Timeline-event |date={{Start date|2023|12|15|df=y}} |event= [[Big Carl|World's largest crane]] places {{convert|47|m|ft|abbr=on|adj=mid|-wide}} dome onto Hinkley Point C's first reactor building<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.edfenergy.com/media-centre/big-carls-spectacular-dome-lift-caps-year-hinkley-point-c |title=Big Carl's spectacular dome lift caps the year at Hinkley Point C|publisher=EDF|date=2023-12-15|access-date=28 January 2024|archive-date=28 January 2024|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20240128180411/https://www.edfenergy.com/media-centre/big-carls-spectacular-dome-lift-caps-year-hinkley-point-c |url-status=live}}</ref>}}<ref>{{cite web |title=On time and built 30% faster – major lift milestone for Hinkley Point C's second reactor |url=https://www.edfenergy.com/energy/nuclear-new-build-projects/hinkley-point-c/news-views/major-lift-milestone-for-hinkley-point-c-second-reactor |website=EDF Energy |access-date=15 September 2020 |date=14 September 2020 |archive-date=15 September 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915173343/https://www.edfenergy.com/energy/nuclear-new-build-projects/hinkley-point-c/news-views/major-lift-milestone-for-hinkley-point-c-second-reactor |url-status=live }}</ref>
* {{Timeline-event |date={{Start date|2024|02|08|df=y}} |event= [[National Grid (Great Britain)|National Grid]] has performed 4 million [[man-hour]]s of work upgrading the grid around HPC.<ref>{{cite web |title=National Grid celebrates 4 million hours worked on the Hinkley Connection Project {{!}} National Grid Group |url=https://www.nationalgrid.com/national-grid-celebrates-4-million-hours-worked-hinkley-connection-project |website=www.nationalgrid.com |date=8 February 2024}}</ref> A 174-tonne 400{{nbsp}}kV supergrid transformer was sent from Rotterdam up the [[river Parrett]] to upgrade the [[Bridgwater]] substation in Somerset.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Mavrokefalidis |first1=Dimitris |title=Giant transformers delivered to boost electricity network |url=https://www.energylivenews.com/2024/06/21/giant-transformers-delivered-to-boost-electricity-network/ |website=Energy Live News |date=21 June 2024}}</ref>}}
