==1980s PWR proposal==
An earlier proposal for a Hinkley Point C power station was made by the [[Central Electricity Generating Board]] (CEGB) in the 1980s for a sister power station to Sizewell B, using the same [[pressurised water reactor]] design, at a cost of £1.7{{nbsp}}billion.<ref>{{Cite journal|url=https://api.parliament.uk/historic-hansard/lords/1990/mar/01/electricity-generating-capacity-nuclear |title=Electricity Generating Capacity: Nuclear Power |date=1 March 1990 |id=HL Deb 1 March 1990 vol 516 cc828-30 |journal=[[Hansard]] |access-date=9 June 2009 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121002103048/http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/lords/1990/mar/01/electricity-generating-capacity-nuclear |archive-date= 2 October 2012 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wiseinternational.org/node/284 |title=In brief{{nbsp}}— Hinkley "approved" |publisher=World Information Service on Energy |date=14 September 1990 |access-date=30 December 2013 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230233013/http://www.wiseinternational.org/node/284 |archive-date=30 December 2013 }}</ref> This proposal obtained planning permission in 1990 following a public inquiry,<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.constructionnews.co.uk/archive/14sep90-uk-hinkley-c-nuclear-power-station-given-planning-permission-13-09-1990/ |title=Hinkley C Nuclear Power Station given planning permission |date=14 September 1990 |publisher=Construction News |access-date=17 November 2009 |archive-date=13 January 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200113124645/https://www.constructionnews.co.uk/archive/14sep90-uk-hinkley-c-nuclear-power-station-given-planning-permission-13-09-1990/ |url-status=live }}</ref> but was dropped as uneconomic in the early 1990s when the electric power industry was privatised and low [[interest rate]] government finance was no longer available.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.parliament.uk/documents/upload/postpn208.pdf|title=The nuclear energy option in the UK|date=December 2003|id=postnote 208|publisher=[[Parliamentary Office of Science and Technology]]|access-date=9 June 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060103235611/http://www.parliament.uk/documents/upload/postpn208.pdf|archive-date=3 January 2006}}</ref>

